setCurrentIndex(0): Switches the QStackedWidget view back to the very first page (index 0), which is your main menu.

removeWidget: Detaches the active game screen (self.hra_widget) from the stack so that old games don't pile up in the background.

deleteLater(): Safely tells Qt to destroy the widget and free up system memory once the current event loop finishes, 
preventing memory leaks when users repeatedly start and leave games.
